  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, to my opinion, only-- he was only half Jewish, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The day before we emigrated, a very young physicist [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] was visiting Dad in our apartment in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Houterman, H-O-U-T-E-R-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was sent by [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another physicist, Max Von Laue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a German Christian, Max Von Laue, also a physicist from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Daddy was supposed to take a very important message to American friends, saying that they are trying to hinder the work to make an atomic bomb.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Heisenberg, who was one of the very famous physicists in Berlin, was under great pressure and felt that it was almost not possible to delay the work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he warned American friends through Daddy, please tell them to accelerate the work there if-- here, if they have done so before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was, of course, a message which Dad had to carry by heart, because it was too dangerous to write it down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because if Dad would have been captured and we all would have been captured, it would have been a terrible danger, and also for Houterman himself.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
